00:28:35.790 --> 00:28:36.730
Tak teruk.

00:29:17.200 --> 00:29:18.180
Tuan, mangkuk lain!

00:29:23.440 --> 00:29:24.730
Cik, lihat.

00:29:41.070 --> 00:29:43.250
Bagaimanakah Zhang Heng, komander Pejabat Peronda Ibu Kota,

00:29:43.350 --> 00:29:45.010
dan Lu Qi, timbalan komander Pengawal Imperial,

00:29:45.750 --> 00:29:47.460
berakhir bersama begitu?

00:29:51.900 --> 00:29:54.380
[Ronda Perhimpunan Imperial]

00:29:56.980 --> 00:29:57.980
[Lu Qi, timbalan komander Pengawal Imperial]

00:29:57.980 --> 00:29:59.100
[Zhang Heng, komander Pejabat Peronda Ibu Kota]

00:30:01.790 --> 00:30:03.010
Peronda Majlis Diraja

00:30:03.030 --> 00:30:04.860
sentiasa dikendalikan oleh Li Hongqing.

00:30:04.960 --> 00:30:05.730
